(10, 'You enter the security office in KC and seek help.', 'If 100 grams of a milkshake corresponds to 150 calories, if three friends, Ram, Shyam and Rhea share a jumbo milkshake which consists of five servings, and Rhea consumes 75 calories, ?and Ram and Shyam split the rest, what is the consumption in grams of Ram?(1 serving=50 grams)', '100', 'Recreation Centre', 'Snack Point', 'Apoorva Mess', '30.jpg'),
