(12, 'On your way from Apoorva, you see a sickly calf on', 'I share my first name with two US states and my last name is an omen of death. My last name is due to the shape of my tail, but I?m not an animal. My parents are names ?Ghost? and ?red?. I have a rank of 1569300 on a certain scale of hotness due to which I was featured in the Guinness Book of World ', 'HP22B', '', '', '', 'snackpoint.jpg'),
