(14, 'You meet a few friends on your way and decide to accompany them to the cricket ground to find out about the screams but there is no one in the ground. You decide to leave the place and go directly to your block.', 'The horizontal range of a projectile fired at an angle of 15 degrees is found out to be 50 m. what will be the range, if the object is fired at an angle of 45 degrees?', '100', '', '', '', 'deg.jpg'),
