(28, 'Tired of being chased and followed you decide the ', 'A ball weighing 0.370 kg collides with a horizontal light spring of force constant 2N/m. The ball compresses the string from the rest position. What was the speed of ball at the instant of collision, assuming the coefficient of kinetic friction between the ball and horizontal surface is 1.', '10', 'VGT PARK GATE', 'KC', '18th Block Gate', 'def.jpg'),
