(30, 'You continue to make reckless decisions and now yo', 'At certain point in a day, the shadow of a 5 inch toy ?is 8 inch. Shadow of a pole at the same time is found out to be 28 inches long. How tall is the flag pole?', '17.5', '', '', '', 'def.jpg'),
(31, 'You?ve finally reached the VGT park gate and start', 'A car drives straight off the edge of a cliff that is 57m high. The investigator at the scene of the accident notes that the point of impact is 130m from the base of the cliff. How fast was the car travelling when it went over the cliff?', '38', 'ATM , SYNDICATE', 'GO TO ROOM FOR CASH', 'VGT PARK', '37.jpg'),
(32, 'All set to leave manipal, but are you carrying cas', 'You take out a loan of  Rs 7000 and the bank charges you 35 percent compound interest per year. If you don''t pay off any of the loan in 4 years, how much would you owe the bank?(Answer to the nearest penny)', '23250', '', '', '', 'def.jpg'),
